README file for Method 1 in "Statistical analysis and thermodynamics uncover key regulator microRNAs from gene expression data"

General instructions
--------------------

1.- Use the script 'combine_algorithms.plx' on the output of prediction algorithms, to create the database.

2.- Use the script 'enrichment_ud.rb' to evaluate the enrichment of miRNAs in experimental data of up- and downregulated genes.

Run the scripts without arguments to see the detailed help.


